      <div class = "starting">Sexducate represents the result of combining design principles and web technologies to create
        an interactive sexual education resource for the greater San Diego area. It serves to provide
        sexual education without overwhelming the user with superfluous and unnecessary information. Provided
        with an intialized database of medical ailments throughout San Diego area, we sought to bring a
        solution to proper sexual education.
      </div>
      <div class = "title">Motivation</div>
      <p>Although there exists numerous resources for obtaining information relating to STD's, none provide
        an informative yet elegant solution. Also, many of these sites are cluttered with irrelevant information or are
        scientific articles/eBooks hiding behind a paywall.
      </p>
